snippet.title: Velvet Nights – A Classic Jazz Album | Timeless Female Vocals in a 90s Smoky Bar
snippet.description:
Velvet Nights – A Classic Jazz Album | Timeless Female Vocals in a 90s Smoky Bar

 #jazz #classicjazz #smoothjazz #femalecrooner #90sjazz #vintagejazz #smokybar #jazzalbum #latenightjazz #romanticjazz #emotionaljazz #AI
An emotional classic jazz album, with warm, strong and nostalgic female vocals. The 6 songs in the album take you back to the space of small bars in the 90s, where cigarette smoke and yellow lights blend with soft jazz melodies. The album brings a combination of classic jazz and cinematic inspiration, supported by AI technology to recreate a lyrical, deep and enchanting musical space.


✉Contact us: jazzmusicback@gmail.com
